g.text: Initiciates the process of adding a ranking to a job opening
Asks for the id of the job offer to rank candidates for
Inputs the id of the job offer
Asks for the number of extra candidates to add
Inputs the number of extra candidates to add
Asks for the emails of the candidates to rank
Inputs the emails of the candidates to rank
[for each candidate that the user wants to rank]
Asks for the ranking of the candidate
Inputs the ranking of the candidate
creates a ranking for the candidate
[for all the candidates that didnt get ranked (rank = 'rank not recorded')]
creates a ranking for the candidate
informs the user that the rankings were added
